---
title: Creamy Mustard Chicken with mash and pan-fried carrots
description: Juicy roast chicken is coated in a creamy mustard sauce made with softened leeks and lashings of creme fraiche. Creamy mash forms the base of this meal, while tender veg adds that little something extra.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R05_W38_IE_IEXFCLC21707-2_Main_high-5a517257.jpg
